zarkas. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/shanks/teenyknot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/01 1:43:43 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/Sigs/4FrickaNEWlt.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thx info</span><hr size=1> Use group tactics. This is a war, not a duel.<br>
<br>
Be sure you have good communication amongst groups.  Make groups with similar levels.  Have a group leader report to the war lord and also have targets called out clearly.<br>
<br>
Right clickable items?  Aside from pumice (yes even nerfed pumice is better than nothing) and poison I don't really use other clickables, you'll have to ask others about that.  As a warrior though, poison isn't an option of course <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><table border=0 align=left width=100%>
