Sig Gallery</font></a></td>
</tr>
</table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umajestykvz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MajestykVZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/01 1:47:27 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thx info</span><hr size=1> Drop thier healers first. <p>Majestyk, <a href="http://Server3.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse">Rogue</a>, <a href="http://www.talonguard.org/shanks">Shanks</a>, <a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/board.asp?brd=5034">Vallon Zek!</a>

We as Shanks, have chosen the hard path. In the hardness of it, is where we find the glory.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulegnavalsharess.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Legna ValSharess</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/01 2:18:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thx info</span><hr size=1> More important than anything is MR.<br>
<br>
The other team will have an enchanter.<br>
The enchanter will Tashani you<br>
The enchanter will mez you<br>
Other casters will root you.<br>
<br>
So, let me say it again. <br>
MR MR MR MR MR MR<br>
<br>
If they cannot stop you, they cannot kill you.<br>
<br>
You will have healers, let them heal. Take out their clerics and you will win. If your MR is under 120, your dead.<br>
<br>
-L <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udovewhispersilk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dove Whispersilk</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/01 3:07:51 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thx info</span><hr size=1> Even a 120 wont do it if they can land Malo and tashani on you... If by high level you mean lvl 60's they can debuff negitive 84 MR which is unresistable. <p><img src=http://fp.geocities.com/ebonydragon79/dove3.jpg> <BR>
Dove the Silent, rank 60 Assassin of Terris-Thule</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=belphrz>Belph RZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/01 9:03:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thx info</span><hr size=1> In large battles DONT take out their healers first.<br>
Take out their ENCHANTERS first. Even with ultrahigh mr they will suck your clerics dry of mana in a blink. Thats when you have lost the battle before one person of your group is killed.<br>
<br>
Let your enchanters do exactly what I said and protect them as long as possible.<br>
<br>
As soon as the enemy clerics are dry let your chanters keep them dry and let them look for more healers to suck out. Also let them take care for themselves at this point and let the &quot;chanter defenders&quot; join the attack group. Ignore the clerics and kill the other healers. Its piece of cake at that point, as YOU will be healed, your enemy not.<br>
<br>
Congratulations, you won your battle.<br>
<br>
This tactics has worked in more than just one major battle of my main characters guild on RZ. Trust me, if you dont have extremely skilled opponents they will die.<br>
<br>
<br>
Cu on RZ<br>
Belph <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usynide3.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Synide3</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/01 8:04:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: thx info</span><hr size=1> If it's that big, do Enchanters, then shamans(so they dont' get malo off on everyone) and mages, mages drop fast.  Shiny brass idols help. Every resist 150+ heh... Dual weilding is nice, because you're not going to be 1on1'ing very often, so you want to stay in range for however long you can. Golem wands, old school pumice own the arena. Items like jboots, shrunken gob skull earrings for dispell(crap buffs) work well also. <p><b>Synide Kiwifury</b>
